---
title: Almond Crusted Hake with roast potatoes and tomato salad
description: The crunchy, herby, savoury almond crust truly is a delightful addition to the golden baked fish in this nutritious and hearty dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R11_W14_IE_IEXCF0175-2_Main_high_switch_salad-f22f228c.jpg
